        <abstract> 
<p>Comments on discussion of residual organs in <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> [ch. 1].</p> 
            <p>Describes his ability to contract the platysma myoides at will.</p>
            <p>Suggests reason for loss of voluntary movement of ears in men and monkeys.</p>
